jobs.html:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Grupo QuintoAndar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are Grupo QuintoAndar, the largest real estate ecosystem in Latin America. Guided by a shared purpose of helping people love where they live, we have a diversified portfolio of brands and solutions across different countries in Latin America, covering all phases of the housing journey. We also have a Technology Hub in Portugal. We develop technology and innovation to transform and enhance the overall living experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the support of a world-class team of investors and advisors, including Kaszek, Qualcomm, General Atlantic, and SoftBank, Grupo QuintoAndar is currently valued at over USD 5.1 billion and continues to grow year over year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here, you will work with top professionals in the market, in an environment that breathes innovation, collaboration, and high performance. To learn more about our story, visit:&lt;a href=&quot;https://grupoquintoandar.com/pt/&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://grupoquintoandar.com/pt/&quot;&gt;https://grupoquintoandar.com/pt/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location &amp;amp; Remote Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our technology team operates under a &quot;remote-first&quot; model, which means we work from home and can live anywhere in Brazil. We also offer the option of working from our São Paulo offices or partner coworking spaces, up to twice a week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hiring Process Stages&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The stages of our hiring processes aim to assess your experiences and allow you to meet our teams and explore career opportunities. They are structured as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Application&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interview with Recruiter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tech Screening&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Interview with Data Team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Science at QuintoAndar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join our Data Science and Machine Learning team and become a key part of our product team, delivering features that enrich our product and uphold the first-class experience we&#39;re known for. You&#39;ll collaborate with talented individuals from various disciplines: Data Scientists, Machine Learning Engineers, Software Engineers, Product Managers, Designers, and more.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Get ready for the job of a lifetime — expect challenging tasks, high standards, meaningful conversations, and outstanding productivity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We tackle problems like pricing and liquidity models, credit, income, and collection models, and developing a platform that allows us to create and deploy these solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect, develop and deploy machine learning systems to production. The main use cases are related to house pricing and liquidity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and execute experiments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze a wide variety of data (structured and unstructured, observational and experimental) to improve current models or create new ones;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate actively in discussions and decisions regarding the whole Data Science chapter (Guilds, Design Reviews, Demos, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we are looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People that are seeking to deliver real impact through Data Science and Machine Learning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of machine learning concepts: regression and classification, clustering, neural networks, feature selection, cross-validation, bias-variance tradeoff, model explainability, etc.;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practical experience with tabular data, preferably in the industry;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good understanding of the engineering challenges to deploy machine learning systems to production;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Python;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal technical communication skills;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good English skills (verbal and written) are mandatory, as it is the official language within the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You&#39;ll stand out if you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a MSc. (or Undergrad + intense experience) in machine learning, data science, statistics, or other relevant fields;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have solid experience with credit, pricing or liquidity models;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience working at fast-growing startups.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Important&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our hiring process starts with the application! If you truly want to be part of our team, please complete this step of the process. We analyze all candidates individually and provide feedback to all applicants.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All communication will be conducted via email, so please stay tuned for our messages and release the domain @quintoandar.com.br to ensure our emails are not sent to spam.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Profit sharing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meal allowance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dental plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Childcare subsidy and Atypical Parenthood subsidy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wellhub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Home office allowance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee assistance program (mental health, social, legal, and financial support)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extended parental leave&lt;/li&gt;
