&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Profit sharing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meal allowance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dental plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Childcare subsidy and Atypical Parenthood subsidy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wellhub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Home office allowance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee assistance program (mental health, social, legal, and financial support)&lt;/li&gt;
