&lt;p&gt;The Grupo QuintoAndar operates in compliance with privacy and data protection laws, including, but not limited to, the Brazilian General Personal Data Protection Law (LGPD) (Law No. 13,709/2018), and ensures the security of your data. To learn more, please access our&lt;a href=&quot;https://carreiras.quintoandar.com.br/aviso-de-privacidade-para-pessoas-candidatas/&quot;&gt; Privacy Notice for Candidates&lt;/a&gt;. For questions or to exercise your rights as a data subject, please contact us through our&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cognitoforms.com/QuintoAndarcom/LeiGeralDeProte%C3%A7%C3%A3oDeDadosPessoaisLGPD&quot;&gt; Service Channel&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

