&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;About the MLE Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;At QuintoAndar we use Machine Learning (ML) to build delightful experiences and solve complex problems. We are at a maturity level where scaling those ML systems is also a challenge. We need Machine Learning Engineers to bring great models to production as effective ML-based products and features, and also evolve this ecosystem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;You can learn more about our ML pipeline and platform&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/quintoandar-tech-blog/machine-learning-pipeline-at-quintoandar-e2f24136006b&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/quintoandar-tech-blog/butterfree-a-spark-based-framework-for-feature-store-building-48c3640522c7&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. Or play a bit with Butterfree &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/quintoandar/butterfree&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; and discover how features are transformed to our Feature Store.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
