&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Assure health and quality of ML services;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Foster best practices for infrastructure and coding regarding machine learning specific requirements;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
