&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Our hiring process starts with the application! If you genuinely want to be part of our team, please complete this step of the process. We analyze all candidates individually and provide feedback to all applicants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;All communication will be conducted via email, so please stay tuned for our messages and release the domain @quintoandar.com.br to ensure our emails are not sent to spam.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
